<div id="review_3655127201" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3655127201" />
    <a title="Marcus Goncalves" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/68801416-marcus-goncalves"><img alt="Marcus Goncalves" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1576034361p2/68801416.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3655127201?book_show_action=true">May 23, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Marcus Goncalves" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Marcus Goncalves" href="/user/show/68801416-marcus-goncalves">Marcus Goncalves</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/39874649-o-p-o-nu">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3655127201" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10934084391459403542">Incredible (and often crude!) story of a very poor young Moroccan kid into his adolescence told during the occupation and the miserable years it brought to that part of the world, West Africa, which to some extent still rings true for many 21st century maroccan youth.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


